other_tests.findings: Transabdominal ultrasound demonstrates the uterus measuring 7.3 x 6.0 x 6.2 cm. Within the fundus is a 4.5 x 3.5 x 4.1 cm fibroid. The endometrium measures 4 mm in thickness and shows no abnormal vascularity. Within the right adnexa is a dilated tubular structure measuring 3.8 x 2.4 x 4.7 cm without appreciable internal debris or echogenicity. The right ovary is not enlarged and shows normal-appearing arterial and venous waveforms. The left ovary is not visualized.
